import React from "react";
import {
  Button,
  Form,
  Grid,
  Header,
  Image,
  Message,
  Segment,
} from "semantic-ui-react";
import AgoraLogo from "../../images/logo.png";

export const Login = () => (
  <>
    <Header as="h2" color="teal" textAlign="center">
      <Image src={AgoraLogo} />
      Agora
    </Header>
    <Form size="large">
      <Segment stacked>
        <Form.Input
          fluid
          icon="user"
          iconPosition="left"
          placeholder="E-mail address"
          id="email"
        />
        <Form.Input
          fluid
          icon="lock"
          iconPosition="left"
          placeholder="Password"
          type="password"
          id="password"
        />

        <Button color="teal" fluid size="large">
          Login
        </Button>
      </Segment>
    </Form>
  </>
);
